===Noun===
'''söndag''' ''c'' (''plural'' [[söndagar]], ''definite singular'' [[söndagen]], ''definite plural'' [[söndagarna]], ''genitive singular'' [[söndags]], ''genitive singular definite'' [[söndagens]], ''genitive plural'' [[söndagars]], ''genitive plural definite'' [[söndagarnas]])

# [[Sunday]]. The seventh day of the [[week]] (according to the [[ISO]] 8601 [[standard]]).

====Etymology====
The word is originally a short form for ''solens dag'', meaning ''day of the [[w:sun|sun]]''. 


